      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TACTIQUE (4) finished second last start in a Group Three feature won by Shine Like Me over 1660m at this track, beaten 6 metres. Drawn well so a win is on the cards in this easier race. JEWEL REASON (5) comes here fresh from a third in the same race as the top selection last start. Ideally placed and rates well as a leading chance. GENUINE STAR (2) faces the starter for the first time. By Art Major and hails from the Grant Dixon stable. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Trial winner who looks above average and is worth considering. FAN THE FLAME (3) lines up for the first time. She is a well bred by Bettors Delight and hails from the Grant Dixon stable. Sure to enjoy an economical run from this draw. Was not far away in a recent trial and has the right credentials to play a major role.",
